"{\"uid\": \"siasat.com-2024-paris-olympics-turkish-shooter-yusuf-dikec-goes-viral-for-winning-silver-find-out-why-3071811\", \"text\": \"In a stunning display of skill and composure, 51-year-old Turkish shooter Yusuf Dike\\u00e7 clinched a silver medal in the mixed team 10-meter air pistol event at the2024 Paris Olympics, all while using remarkably limited equipment. Competing alongside Sevval Ilayda Tarhan, Dike\\u00e7 stood out by forgoing specialized shooting goggles and ear protection, opting instead for regular prescription glasses and simple earplugs.  Dike\\u00e7's unconventional approach, including shooting with one hand in his pocket, captivated audiences and led to his viral status on social media, with one image garnering over 21 million views.  Social media reacted explosively to Turkish shooter Yusuf Dike\\u00e7's silver medal win at the 2024 Paris Olympics, quickly turning him into a viral sensation.  A photo capturing this moment went viral, racking up over 62 million views on X (formerly Twitter). Users flooded the platform with memes and jokes, humorously suggesting that Turkey had sent a \\\"covert spy\\\" to the Olympics and that Dike\\u00e7 intentionally avoided winning gold to maintain a low profile.  insane aura51-yr old Yusuf Dikec of Turkey shows up to the Olympics for shooting without special lenses\\u2026without ear protection\\u2026hand in his pocket & both eyes open\\u2026and casually takes home a silver medalpic.twitter.com/qRB3kwRZmz  FAANG Engineer vs. Startup Founderpic.twitter.com/6hDpJRBlBA  I am gonna tell my kids these were the Avengerspic.twitter.com/LtxdFUxbpS  Currently the most famous man in the worldpic.twitter.com/srxPhwDkUk  South Korea sent a fully-kitted out player for the Olympic shooting.Turkey sent an guy with no specialized lenses, eye cover or ear protection and got the silver medalpic.twitter.com/8xJOr9qCPf  Turkey sent a 51 yr old guy with no specialized lenses, eye cover or ear protection and got the silver medal